- either refuse EEC type approval or the issue of the document provided for in the third indent of Article 10 (1) of Council Directive 70/156/EEC (3), or national type approval, for a type of vehicle,
- or prohibit the entry into service of vehicles,
if the rear-view mirrors of that type of vehicle or vehicles comply with the provisions of this Directive.
