The preparation belonging to the group "Micro-organisms" listed in Annex II to the present Regulation may be authorised according to Directive 70/524/EEC as additive in animal nutrition under the conditions laid down in the said Annex.
Article 3
This Regulation shall enter into force on the day of its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities.
